  <h1>Irrigator - LCD Version</h1>

  <p>The LCD version of the Irrigator device is designed for clear and precise monitoring of soil moisture levels, featuring a 1602 LCD display and easy-to-use configuration buttons.</p>

  <img src="/assets/img/device-irrigator.jpg" alt="LCD Version" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
  
  <h3>Key Features</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Waterproof soil moisture sensor.</li>
    <li>1602 LCD display for clear visual feedback.</li>
    <li>Buttons for sensor calibration and irrigation threshold adjustment.</li>
    <li>Peristaltic pump embedded into the enclosure.</li>
  </ul>

